data.description: Step into the urban oasis designed for effortless modern living. The expansive windows & opaque glass door flood the main floor with natural light throughout. Revel in the combination of engineered hardwoods on the main floor & plush carpeting in the bedrooms. Each bedroom comes complete with its own private bathroom, offering convenience & privacy. This property boasts low-maintenance landscaping, generous cabinet space, & an expansive roof deck with stunning northeast views of Lake WA. The location is unbeatable, with an impressive 90 Walk Score, providing easy access to public transit, a plethora of parks, delightful eateries, inviting coffee shops! Don't miss the chance to own this urban haven! Eligible for BofA down payment program.
